<h3 id="channelpipeline处理器责任链">ChannelPipeline：处理器责任链</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">ChannelPipeline中的数据流向：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">入站（Inbound：读取数据）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  Socket → HeadContext → LoggingHandler → StringDecoder → BusinessHandler → TailContext
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                                           ↑
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">                                                      业务处理
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">出站（Outbound：写入数据）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  BusinessHandler → StringEncoder → LoggingHandler → HeadContext → Socket
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       ↑
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  ctx.writeAndFlush(response)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">注意：Inbound从头到尾，Outbound从尾到头</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
